 get phone calls and letters from consumers in cities where bai is not yet on the shelf asking for the product said ben weiss founder and ceo bai brands our relationship with dr pepper snapple group will allow us to rapidly rollout bai to new markets and into the hands of those consumers we have tested the bai brand in select markets with great success over the last several quarters said jeff conrad vice president of market development for dps there is no question that bai fits exceedingly well with our portfolio of leading brands and we expect this new choice to be very well received by consumers from coast to coast recent new marquee retailers which will be serviced by bai and dr pepper snapple group include marketleaders such as jewelosco stop  shop duane reade and safeway plus more than  additional costco stores throughout the country over many years dps has expertly assembled what we feel is the most competitive route to market for beverages in this country said ken kurtz president of bai brands the great taste all natural ingredients and use of the coffeefruit as a source of antioxidants are driving strong consumer demand for bai and so we are very pleased to work with dps to complete our national distribution footprint about bai brands llc bai brands llc makers of bai calorie antioxidant infusions is a princetonbased company founded in august  by entrepreneur and coffee industry pioneer ben weiss bai calorie antioxidant infusions are only five calories infused with coffeefruit and flavored with exotic fruit juices they are naturally sweetened gluten free kosher vegan soy bpa and gmofree for more information about the line of eight bai  antioxidant infusions and the brand named by beverage world among the breakout brands of  visit drinkbaicom about dr pepper snapple group dr pepper snapple group nyse dps is a leading producer of flavored beverages in north america and the caribbean our success is fueled by more than  brands that are synonymous with refreshment